		<table class="contentpaneopen">
				<tr>
			<td valign="top" colspan="2">
				<table border="0" cellspacing="15" cellpadding="2" width="100%" style="vertical-align: top"><tbody><tr><td style="border: 1px solid #dddddd; background: #ffffff none repeat scroll 0% 0%; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial; vertical-align: top; width: 95%; height: 60px"><div class="featureheader">&nbsp;Property Information</div><div style="margin: 2px; padding: 5px; overflow: auto; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; position: relative; top: -14px"><span class="contentdescription">Search for property in the City of Atlanta by address or tax parcel ID and view information&nbsp;such as&nbsp;zoning district, flood hazard, and market value. Link to an interactive map and bird&#39;s eye view of property.&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/gishome/index.php?option=com_content&amp;task=view&amp;id=14&amp;Itemid=49">more</a></span> </div></td></tr><tr><td style="border: 1px solid #dddddd; background: #ffffff none repeat scroll 0% 0%; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial; vertical-align: top; width: 95%; height: 80px"><div class="featureheader">Interactive Maps</div><div style="margin: 2px; padding: 5px; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; position: relative; top: -14px"><span class="contentdescription">Interactively view maps of the City. Choose which geographic features you want to see; query the map for details about features; generate report; do your own customized mark-ups with labels and highlighting; generate PDFs of your customized maps for emailing or printing.&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/gishome/index.php?option=com_content&amp;task=blogcategory&amp;id=28&amp;Itemid=77">more</a></span> </div></td></tr><tr><td style="border: 1px solid #dddddd; background: #ffffff none repeat scroll 0% 0%; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial; vertical-align: top; width: 95%; height: 80px"><div class="featureheader">Crime Maps</div><div style="margin: 2px; padding: 5px; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; position: relative; top: -14px"><span class="contentdescription">View interactive maps of recent crimes across the City. Customize the map by selecting types of crime and time period. (Note that this is an external website courtesy of the Atlanta Police Department.)&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://www.atlantapd.org/index.asp?nav=CrimeMapping" target="_blank">more</a></span> </div></td></tr><tr><td style="border: 1px solid #dddddd; background: #ffffff none repeat scroll 0% 0%; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial; vertical-align: top; width: 95%; height: 80px"><div class="featureheader">Map Catalog</div><div style="margin: 2px; padding: 5px; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; position: relative; top: -14px"><span class="contentdescription">Browse and view maps from the large collection produced by the City of Atlanta GIS. All maps can be downloaded and printed.&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/gishome/index.php?option=com_content&amp;task=view&amp;id=11&amp;Itemid=44">more</a></span> </div></td></tr><tr><td style="border: 1px solid #dddddd; background: #ffffff none repeat scroll 0% 0%; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial; vertical-align: top; width: 95%; height: 80px"><div class="featureheader">Zoning Maps</div><div class="contentdescription" style="margin: 2px; padding: 5px; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; position: relative; top: -14px">View the offical zoning map sheets by entering an address, tax parcel ID or land lot. Alternatively, use an index map to select a map sheet. The option to view zoning districts in an interactive web map is also provided.&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/gishome/index.php?option=com_content&amp;task=view&amp;id=15&amp;Itemid=50">more</a></div></td></tr><tr><td style="border: 1px solid #dddddd; background: #ffffff none repeat scroll 0% 0%; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial; vertical-align: top; width: 95%; height: 80px"><div class="featureheader">Document Archive</div><div class="contentdescription" style="margin: 2px; padding: 5px; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; position: relative; top: -14px">View official documents such as subdivision plats, zoning applications, and site maps. Search for documents by keyword. All documents are provided as PDFs and can be freely downloaded and printed.&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/gishome/index.php?option=com_content&amp;task=view&amp;id=12&amp;Itemid=48">more</a></div></td></tr></tbody></table>			</td>
		</tr>
